/* ========================= README ========================= */
# Multi-User Video Chat App (Deploy-Ready)

## Features
- Multi-user video/audio chat via WebRTC
- Real-time text chat via Socket.io
- Dynamic rooms with custom Room IDs
- Ready to deploy: Vercel frontend + Heroku/Render backend

## Setup
### Backend (Heroku/Render)
```bash
cd backend
npm install
heroku create your-backend-app
git push heroku main
```
Set environment variable `FRONTEND_URL` to your frontend deployment URL.

### Frontend (Vercel)
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
vercel
```
Set `REACT_APP_BACKEND_URL` in `.env` to your backend deployment URL.

### Running Locally
1. Backend: `cd backend && npm install && npm start`
2. Frontend: `cd frontend && npm install && npm start`
Open multiple tabs at http://localhost:3000 and join the same Room ID.
